{"tid":384221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★養兒防老？為助兒子上車  耗盡所有積蓄，還將自住單位加按","createTime":"2017-09-02T06:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T08:14:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ed748845b9bbb0ede6e36eead150a529895bd238","tid":384221,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:36:29.000Z","msg":"老伙記明言希望可繼續做下去，並願意做一個工作時間比較長、收入比較少的崗位。老伙記原來是幫助了兒子上車，做了「父幹一族」，不但耗盡所有積蓄，還將自住單位加按，銀行不接受將退休人士申請，要繼續做幾年才會批核按揭，老伙記只有放下尊嚴，希望可獲續聘。<br />\n<br />\n湯文亮指，其友人陷入進退兩難，老伙記如果重回工作崗位，一定對新人做成壓力，甚至令公司分化，而且，老伙記明顯為錢而工作，不繼續聘用，得不到銀行貸款，除損失巨額金錢外，甚至令他們父子反目。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170902/bkn-20170902124901322-0902_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170902%2Fbkn-20170902124901322-0902_00842_001.html&d=V3zUvmTWh0Hw1QfT8m4wI8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=d372ad37\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170902/bkn-20170902124901322-0902_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"04e8c8d9317001faa1e3c7a1a9d856cc9b301e7a","tid":384221,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488964fa92cf62825b5e5ad21f0fdbaf53a53444","tid":384221,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:37:41.000Z","msg":"最擔心的不是工作，而是兒子是否可獨立地負責他們新買住宅的供款，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f90e7dee2cfaa97